---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Data Deletion — TopoQuizz"
  description="Learn how to request deletion of your personal data from TopoQuizz."
>
  <Header />

  <main class="privacy-page">
    <div class="privacy-hero">
      <div class="privacy-hero-inner">
        <span class="sec-badge">Legal</span>
        <h1>Data Deletion Request</h1>
        <p>Last updated: April 21, 2026</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="privacy-body">
      <div class="privacy-content">

        <p>
          TopoQuizz, operated by <strong>SHEMED YISRAEL SOFTWARE CREATION LLC</strong>, respects your right
          to have your personal data deleted. This page explains what data we collect, what gets deleted when
          you request it, and how to submit a deletion request.
        </p>

        <h2>1. Data We Collect via Facebook Login</h2>
        <p>
          When you sign in to TopoQuizz using Facebook Login, we may receive and store the following
          information from your Facebook account, subject to the permissions you granted:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Full name</li>
          <li>Email address</li>
          <li>Facebook user ID</li>
          <li>Basic profile information (profile picture, locale)</li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          This information is used solely to create and manage your TopoQuizz account. We do not use it
          for advertising targeting or share it with third parties beyond what is described in our
          <a href="/privacy">Privacy Policy</a>.
        </p>

        <h2>2. What Gets Deleted</h2>
        <p>When we process a data deletion request, we delete or anonymize:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Your account profile (name, email, Facebook user ID)</li>
          <li>Your quiz history, scores, and progress</li>
          <li>Saved content, favorites, and avatar selection</li>
          <li>Any other personal data associated with your account</li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          We may retain certain non-personal or aggregated data that cannot be linked back to you, and data
          we are legally required to retain for compliance, fraud prevention, or dispute resolution purposes.
        </p>

        <h2>3. How to Request Deletion</h2>
        <p>To request deletion of your data, send an email to:</p>

        <div class="deletion-cta">
          <div class="deletion-cta-inner">
            <div class="deletion-icon">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <rect width="20" height="16" x="2" y="4" rx="2"/><path d="m22 7-8.97 5.7a1.94 1.94 0 0 1-2.06 0L2 7"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="deletion-label">Send your request to</p>
              <a href="mailto:administracion@shemayisraelsrl.com" class="deletion-email">
                administracion@shemayisraelsrl.com
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <p>Include the following in your email:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Subject line: <strong>"Data Deletion Request — TopoQuizz"</strong></li>
          <li>The email address associated with your account</li>
          <li>Confirmation that you wish to permanently delete your account and data</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>4. Processing Time</h2>
        <p>
          We will acknowledge your request within <strong>5 business days</strong> and complete the
          deletion within <strong>30 days</strong> of receiving your request. We will send a confirmation
          email once the deletion is complete.
        </p>

        <h2>5. Contact</h2>
        <p>For any questions about this process, contact us at:</p>
        <address>
          <strong>SHEMED YISRAEL SOFTWARE CREATION LLC</strong><br />
          4851 W Hillsboro Blvd Ste A3<br />
          Pompano Beach, FL 33073<br />
          United States<br />
          Email: <a href="mailto:administracion@shemayisraelsrl.com">administracion@shemayisraelsrl.com</a>
        </address>

      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

  <Footer appStoreUrl="#" playStoreUrl="#" />
</Layout>

<style>
  .privacy-page {
    min-height: 100vh;
  }

  .privacy-hero {
    background: linear-gradient(121deg, #3b4d6d 0%, var(--blue) 60%, var(--blue-mid) 100%);
    padding: 72px 0 64px;
  }

  .privacy-hero-inner {
    max-width: 860px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 80px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 16px;
  }

  .privacy-hero h1 {
    font-family: "Plus Jakarta Sans", sans-serif;
    font-size: 48px;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--white);
    line-height: 1.15;
  }

  .privacy-hero p {
    color: var(--blue-light);
    font-size: 14px;
  }

  .privacy-body {
    padding: 64px 0 96px;
    background: var(--bg);
  }

  .privacy-content {
    max-width: 860px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 80px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 20px;
  }

  .privacy-content p {
    color: var(--teal);
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .privacy-content h2 {
    font-family: "Plus Jakarta Sans", sans-serif;
    font-size: 22px;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--navy);
    margin-top: 20px;
    padding-bottom: 10px;
    border-bottom: 1.5px solid var(--blue-pale);
  }

  .privacy-content ul {
    padding-left: 20px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 6px;
  }

  .privacy-content li {
    color: var(--teal);
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .privacy-content a {
    color: var(--blue);
    text-decoration: underline;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }

  .privacy-content a:hover {
    color: var(--navy);
  }

  .privacy-content strong {
    color: var(--navy);
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .deletion-cta {
    background: var(--white);
    border: 2px solid var(--blue-pale);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 24px 28px;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(40, 49, 67, 0.05);
  }

  .deletion-cta-inner {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 16px;
  }

  .deletion-icon {
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    background: var(--blue-pale);
    border-radius: 12px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    color: var(--blue);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .deletion-label {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--teal);
    margin: 0 0 4px 0;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .deletion-email {
    font-family: "Plus Jakarta Sans", sans-serif;
    font-size: 17px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--blue);
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .deletion-email:hover {
    color: var(--navy);
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  address {
    font-style: normal;
    background: var(--white);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 24px 28px;
    color: var(--teal);
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 2;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(40, 49, 67, 0.05);
  }

  address strong {
    display: block;
    font-family: "Plus Jakarta Sans", sans-serif;
    font-size: 16px;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .privacy-hero-inner,
    .privacy-content {
      padding: 0 20px;
    }

    .privacy-hero {
      padding: 48px 0 40px;
    }

    .privacy-hero h1 {
      font-size: 32px;
    }

    .privacy-body {
      padding: 48px 0 72px;
    }

    .deletion-cta-inner {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 12px;
    }
  }
</style>
